data.description: Step into an updated and spacious home situated in the coveted Gretna East High School zone with Falling Waters Elem in the neighborhood. This home boasts a fully finished basement and open floorplan. The heated and cooled garage ensures your comfort in any season, complemented by an extra parking driveway for all your guests. Outside, the large patio offers a serene escape or a lively entertainment area. Enjoy the proximity to an amazing local park featuring a playground, walking trail, basketball and pickleball courts, and more, providing endless outdoor activities. Don't miss out on this perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community. AMA
